Heliolisk (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0694: Helioptile
Pokémon
#0696: Tyrunt →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Heliolisk (TCG Pocket).

Heliolisk has been featured on 13 different cards since it debuted in the Flashfire expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Heliolisk cards are normally Lightning-type or Colorless-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Heliolisk

Heliolisk
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
